---
title: Honey-Soy Pork Belly & Stir-Fried Greens with Garlic Rice & Peanuts
description: What’s an instant way to bring bold, international flavours to pork? Add this sweet ‘n’ salty honey-soy sauce to melt-in-your-mouth pork belly. Teamed with sticky veggies, plus an aromatic garlic rice, this meal will make your tastebuds sing!

